-- Cameron to Host Merkel Next Week for Talks on Economy, Financial System
-- B y   T o n y   C z u c z k a
-- 2010-10-22T09:44:50Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-22/cameron-to-host-merkel-next-week-for-talks-on-economy-financial-system.html
British Prime Minister David Cameron
will host German Chancellor Angela Merkel for talks on economic
and financial topics on Oct. 30, a German government spokeswoman
said. They will meet at Chequers, the country residence of
British prime ministers, spokeswoman Sabine Heimbach told
reporters in Berlin today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Tony Czuczka at 
 aczuczka@bloomberg.net  